Api_lib 2026
commit: `www.github.com/jjcdev/library`

<----- ROUTES ----->

===> ROUTES PUBLIQUES
Login (connexion): /api_lib/login
    Method: POST
    body:{
        username: String,
        password: String
    }

    Réponse: {
            success: boolean,
            message: String
        }

Signup (inscription): /api_lib/signup
    Method: POST
    body:{
        firstname: String(10),
        lastName: String(10),
        password: String(15)
    }

    Réponse: {
            success: boolean,
            message: String
        }

===> ROUTES PRIVEES (après connexion)

** Au chargement de la page **
List : /api_lib/list
Description: Liste de touts les livres présents dans la bibli
Method: GET
    body:{
        accessToken:String
    }

    Réponse:{
        {
            id: String,
            title: String,
            author: String,
            editingYear: INTEGER,
            size:INTEGER,
            repositoryBy: String
        }
    }

** Commandes **
Add : api_lib/add
Description: Ajouter un livre
Method: POST
    body:{
        title: String,
        author: String,
        editingYear: INTEGER,
        repositoryBy: String
    }